there are two phases in execution of memory 
1.memory creation phases
2. execution phase

i. while running a code first of code run through global execution or enviroment and its allocated inside 
-'this'
ii. memory creation phase :here all varible name store and put there value undefined
name ->undefined 
incase of function -> it store function defination ----this is first cycle next we have

iii. execution phase: give the value to the keys 
like name->"suman", age->18 in this way

